Plot data from files or stdin.

Input data from a file (argv) or stdin may be in the format written by (plot.Plots).Encode
or in the simpler data-only plot.TextDataFormat

The widget is interactive (double click, zoom, pan)
A slider is connected to slide through a dataset after highlight.
A table can be associated with the data, which shows in a list box below (called "Caption").

Win32-only (using lxn/walk)